<pb ed="T" id="T21.1310.0457b" n="0457b"/>
<lb n="0457b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0457b02"/><head type="no">No. 1310</head>
<lb n="0457b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0457003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享和二年刊長谷寺藏本</note>北斗七星護摩法<note n="0457004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔複熾盛光法〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457004"><lem><note place="inline">複熾盛光法</note></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0457b04"/>
<lb n="0457b05"/><byline type="Author">一行撰</byline>
<lb n="0457b06"/><div1 type="other"><p>能吉祥真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457b07"/><p type="dharani">曩莫羅怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>曩莫素麼
<lb n="0457b08"/>薩羅&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>諾譏灑<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">引</note>若<note place="inline">上</note>野者
<lb n="0457b09"/><note place="inline">去</note>&CB00418;地波阿<note place="inline">去引</note>路迦囉野怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他弩摩
<lb n="0457b10"/>底跛弩摩底薩賓&CB00135;佉<note place="inline">上</note>細娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457b11"/><p>北斗七星印　左右二火二空相係捻之二水
<lb n="0457b12"/>合指前面二地二風張立即成印<note place="inline">出阿陀蜜經或在口決云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0457b13"/><p>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457b14"/><p type="dharani">唵颯哆<note n="0457005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曩〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457005"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>而<note place="inline">齒伊反</note>曩野伴惹<note n="0457006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457006"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">密</rdg></app>惹野<note place="inline">二合</note>野
<lb n="0457b15"/>染普他摩沙&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>弭曩<note place="inline">名位</note>囉訖<note n="0457007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">山＝仙&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457007"><lem>山</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">仙</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;
<lb n="0457b16"/><note place="inline">二合</note>都娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457b17"/><p>日天印　先合掌風以下四指頭相拄前方大
<lb n="0457b18"/>開二空各著風側真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457b19"/><p type="dharani">曩莫囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅夜<note place="inline">引</note>野曩莫素哩野薩
<lb n="0457b20"/>&CB00085;曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉惹野唵阿謨伽寫野
<lb n="0457b21"/><note place="inline">名位</note>設底<note place="inline">去</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457b22"/><p>月天印　定手火空相捻餘直&CB00594;如持蓮華真
<lb n="0457b23"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457b24"/><p type="dharani">唵戰<note place="inline">上</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合引</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉惹<note n="0457008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＋（唵阿謨伽寫野）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457008"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">野唵阿謨伽寫野</rdg></app>
<lb n="0457b25"/><note place="inline">名位</note>設底娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457b26"/><p>南方火星印　左手作拳安腰左右手五指直
<lb n="0457b27"/>&CB00594;相著屈空納著掌中風屈中節與娑&CB00085;訶相
<lb n="0457b28"/>招真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457b29"/><p type="dharani">唵阿&CB00344;囉迦<note n="0457009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457009"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>魯<note place="inline">名位</note>儗野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1310.0457c" n="0457c"/>
<lb n="0457c01"/><p>北方水天印　右手作拳安腰右左手屈拳空
<lb n="0457c02"/>勿入掌中風直&CB00594;中節少屈真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c03"/><p type="dharani">唵母馱曩乞殺怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02755;曩<note place="inline">名位</note>契
<lb n="0457c04"/>奴<note place="inline">二合</note>摩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457c05"/><p>東方木星印　二手金剛合掌二空直立真言
<lb n="0457c06"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c07"/><p type="dharani">唵婆囉<note place="inline">二合</note>訶薩&CB00425;<note place="inline">二合</note>底曩摩比跢&CB00085;曩<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0457c08"/>野<note place="inline">名位</note>摩&CB00256;&CB00085;囉馱<note place="inline">二合</note>寧娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457c09"/><p>西方金星印　二手合掌二空直立真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c10"/><p type="dharani">唵戍<note place="inline">上</note>羯囉&CB00344;馱&CB00085;<note n="0457010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉二合&CB00085;囉＝二合囉&CB00085;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457010"><lem>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;囉</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">二合囉&CB00085;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>邏惹野<note place="inline">名
<lb n="0457c11"/>位</note>室哩迦哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457c12"/><p>中宮土星印　先合掌風已下四指頭拄前方
<lb n="0457c13"/>大開二空各著風側真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c14"/><p type="dharani">唵捨<note n="0457011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泥＋（吃）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457011"><lem>泥</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">泥吃</rdg></app>殺<note n="0457012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝&CB00135;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0457012"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&CB00135;</rdg></app>囉曩乞殺怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>訶
<lb n="0457c15"/><note place="inline">引</note>摩曩<note place="inline">引</note>嚕婆野<note place="inline">名位</note>普瑟底<note place="inline">二合</note>迦哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0457c16"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0457c17"/><p>羅&CB00264;星印　二手金剛合掌二空直立真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c18"/><p type="dharani">唵囉戶曩阿素<note place="inline">二合</note>羅邏惹野塞摩捨都曩野
<lb n="0457c19"/><note place="inline">名位</note>扇底迦哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457c20"/><p>計都星印　二手合掌二空直立真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c21"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>計都曩<note place="inline">引</note>曩乞殺<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0457c22"/>邏惹野<note place="inline">名位</note>吽娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0457c23"/><p>計都者翻為旗也旗者彗星也羅&CB00264;者交會蝕
<lb n="0457c24"/>神也二隱星木金土都五同用二手合掌二空
<lb n="0457c25"/>直立印。</p>
<lb n="0457c26"/><p>九執曜天總印　真實合掌二空相並直&CB00594;二
<lb n="0457c27"/>風舒各本開立來去總真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0457c28"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00617;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>醯<note place="inline">二</note>濕囉<note place="inline">二合</note>哩耶<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00425;羅&CB00425;哆<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0457c29"/>&CB04313;底<note place="inline">五</note>摩野<note place="inline">六</note>莎賀</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1310.0458a" n="0458a"/>
<lb n="0458a01"/><p>二十八宿總印　堅實合掌並二空直立當心
<lb n="0458a02"/>以二空召之總真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a03"/><p type="dharani">唵諾乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>涅<note place="inline">寧吉反</note>蘇那&CB00135;曳莎賀</p>
<lb n="0458a04"/><p>諸神祇印　右手拳中指頭舒少許屈相召真
<lb n="0458a05"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a06"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;那囉延那也<note n="0458001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醫＝翳&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458001"><lem>醫</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">翳</rdg></app>醯曳<note n="0458002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01217;＝呬&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458002"><lem>&CB01217;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">呬</rdg></app>莎賀</p>
<lb n="0458a07"/><p>延命真言曰先一千遍。</p>
<lb n="0458a08"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>麼折羅喻碎<note place="inline">某甲</note>薩&CB00085;訶</p>
<lb n="0458a09"/><p>塗香印　慧手向外以定手仰握慧手腕當心
<lb n="0458a10"/>如此真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a11"/><p type="dharani">唵尾輸馱獻度納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0458a12"/><p>奉華印　二手內相叉交開仰之二風指側端
<lb n="0458a13"/>相拄空置風邊當心念之真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a14"/><p type="dharani">唵摩訶<note place="inline">引</note>妹怛哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>毘庾<note place="inline">二合</note>訥&CB00617;帝娑婆
<lb n="0458a15"/><note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0458a16"/><p>燒香印　二手中指以下六指背&CB00594;相著二風
<lb n="0458a17"/>舒側端不相著少許也二空置頭指邊當心真
<lb n="0458a18"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a19"/><p type="dharani">唵達麼馱怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>弩&CB00617;帝娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p>
<lb n="0458a20"/><p>奉食印　二手虛合開掌向上如掬之勢當心
<lb n="0458a21"/>念之真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a22"/><p type="dharani">唵阿囉囉迦囉囉末&CB00444;捺娜弭末&CB00444;捺禰摩訶
<lb n="0458a23"/>沫瀝娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p>
<lb n="0458a24"/><p>燈明印　慧手作拳以空端捻火<note n="0458003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">面＋（頭指）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0458003" corr="面頭指" resp="【原】">面</sic>向上奉
<lb n="0458a25"/>供北斗七星本命星并曜宿元辰等真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458a26"/><p type="dharani">唵怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;多<note place="inline">引</note>囉脂<note place="inline">二合</note>娑叵<note place="inline">二合</note>囉儜&CB00085;婆
<lb n="0458a27"/><note place="inline">引</note>娑曩&CB00344;&CB00344;揉<note n="0458004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＋（哩）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458004"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">娜哩</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">二合</note>娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p>
<lb n="0458a28"/><p>普供養印　金剛合掌二頭指<note n="0458005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB04271;＝蹙&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458005"><lem>&CB04271;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">蹙</rdg></app>如寶形並
<lb n="0458a29"/>&CB00594;大指　真言曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1310.0458b" n="0458b"/>
<lb n="0458b01"/><p type="dharani">唵阿謨伽布惹<note place="inline">一</note>麼抳跛納麼<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日&CB00619;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0458b02"/>怛他&CB00617;多尾路枳帝<note place="inline">三</note>三滿多&CB00425;囉薩囉吽</p>
<lb n="0458b03"/><p>讚嘆印　金剛合掌。</p>
<lb n="0458b04"/><p type="dharani">阿演都泥&CB00085;左&CB00344;素囉緊那囉那<note place="inline">上</note>囉乞鑠迦
<lb n="0458b05"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>那野<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達麼&CB00617;哩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0458b06"/>合</note>多地伽囉<note place="inline">三</note>尾達麼左&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>捨麼操企
<lb n="0458b07"/>也<note place="inline">二合引四</note>&CB00135;銘<note place="inline">二合</note>多部多銘多&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>迦捨夜
<lb n="0458b08"/><note place="inline">五</note>怛&CB00135;賀室囉<note place="inline">二合</note>麼拏也馱<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0458b09"/><p>觀爐中有七<tt place="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A642;</t><t lang="chi">嚕</t></tt>字變成北斗七星所謂本命
<lb n="0458b10"/>星置中心六星為伴即&CI0004;合掌向爐啟<note n="0458006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝白&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458006"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">白</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0458b11"/><lg><l>至心奉啟</l><l>北極七星</l><l>貪狼巨門</l>
<lb n="0458b12"/><l>祿存文曲</l><l>廉貞武曲</l><l>破軍尊星</l>
<lb n="0458b13"/><l>為<note place="inline">某甲</note></l><l>災厄解脫</l><l>壽命延長</l>
<lb n="0458b14"/><l>得見百秋</l><l>今作護摩</l><l>唯願尊星</l>
<lb n="0458b15"/><l>降臨此處</l><l>納受護摩</l><l><note n="0458007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刑＝刊&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458007"><lem>刑</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">刊</rdg></app>死厄籍</l>
<lb n="0458b16"/><l>記長壽札</l><l>投華為座</l></lg>
<lb n="0458b17"/><p>結招北斗印　虛心合掌二大指捻二無名指
<lb n="0458b18"/>甲中指如蓮葉形二頭指<note n="0458008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">小＝少&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0458008" corr="少" resp="【原】">小</sic>開屈來去真言
<lb n="0458b19"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0458b20"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多那囉曩翳醯枳頗伊<note place="inline">一</note>賀伊<note place="inline">二</note>那
<lb n="0458b21"/>伊<note place="inline">三</note>加伊<note place="inline">四</note>囉謨囉<note place="inline">五</note>哆囉伽<note place="inline">六</note>伽含<note place="inline">七</note>娑婆
<lb n="0458b22"/><note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0458b23"/><p>想北斗七星來赴　次供養畢　次投華發遣
<lb n="0458b24"/>印　虛心合掌以二大指捻二無名指甲中指
<lb n="0458b25"/>小指如蓮華形二頭指小開屈外撥真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0458b26"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多那囉曩&CB00617;車頗伊賀伊迦伊囉謨
<lb n="0458b27"/>囉多囉伽訶含莎&CB00085;賀<note place="inline">觀想北斗七星等還座本位</note></p>
<lb n="0458b28"/><p>補闕真言</p>
<lb n="0458b29"/><p type="dharani">唵呼嚕呼嚕佐野保計伊娑婆訶</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1310.0458c" n="0458c"/>
<lb n="0458c01"/><p>修此北斗七星護摩法者<note n="0458009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刊＝削&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458009"><lem>刊</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">削</rdg></app>於死籍記長壽
<lb n="0458c02"/>札神驗最明延命增算除災招富延命之法無
<lb n="0458c03"/>如此者也。</p></div1>
<lb n="0458c04"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" n="1" label="北斗法"/><head><note n="0458010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔北斗法〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458010"><lem>北斗法</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0458c05"/><div2 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" n="2" label="熾盛光要法"/><head>熾盛光要法</head>
<lb n="0458c06"/><p>爾時釋迦牟尼佛在淨居天宮告諸天宿曜十
<lb n="0458c07"/>二宮神。我今說過去沙羅王如來真言。若有國
<lb n="0458c08"/>王所居國界五星陵逼二十八宿及帝座每日
<lb n="0458c09"/>晨朝於道場中結印誦此真言七遍。五星諸曜
<lb n="0458c10"/><note n="0458011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陵逼諸座不能＝不能陵逼諸座&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0458011" corr="不能陵逼諸座" resp="【原】">陵逼諸座不能</sic>為災害若火星欲入南斗。應
<lb n="0458c11"/>於一忿怒尊像下點南斗形及點火星於此中
<lb n="0458c12"/>畫彼設&CB00418;嚕形<note place="inline"><note n="0458012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">并＝&CB00308;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0458012"><lem>并</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&CB00308;</rdg></app></note>書名於心上即結印安印
<lb n="0458c13"/>於忿怒像身上誦真言七遍。於娑&CB00085;訶句上加
<lb n="0458c14"/>彼設&CB00418;嚕名忿怒勵聲誦真言所有災禍移去。</p>
<lb n="0458c15"/><p type="dharani">南莫三曼多沒馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底賀哆舍
<lb n="0458c16"/>沙那喃<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">三</note>佉佉<note place="inline">四</note>佉&CB01217;佉&CB01217;<note place="inline">五</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>入
<lb n="0458c17"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;<note place="inline">六</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;&CB00425;
<lb n="0458c18"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">七</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">八</note>瑟致
<lb n="0458c19"/>哩<note place="inline">二合引九</note>薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>吒薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">十</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0458c20"/><p>其印相二手內相叉為拳&CB00594;合二中指各屈頭
<lb n="0458c21"/>指於中指後如金剛杵形以二大指各押中指
<lb n="0458c22"/>第二節文也　此真言一切如來之所加持。名
<lb n="0458c23"/>熾盛威德佛頂真言。能成<app><lem>辦</lem><rdg wit="【大】">辨</rdg></app>八萬種吉祥事。能
<lb n="0458c24"/>除滅八萬種災禍不祥惡夢。若見聞諸不祥事
<lb n="0458c25"/>清淨心誦一遍則不能為害。五星所到諸座位
<lb n="0458c26"/>成陵逼或入或穿過或退行侵陵即於沙頗訶
<lb n="0458c27"/>句上加彼星名。誦真言七遍。命彼五星為善不
<lb n="0458c28"/>能為害。熒惑太白等所到諸宿分野及帝座於
<lb n="0458c29"/>分野宿中如前於像下畫彼惡人形亦損彼人
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1310.0459a" n="0459a"/>
<lb n="0459a01"/>令不起惡意或被羅&CB00264;掩弊日月薄蝕或彗星
<lb n="0459a02"/>現或旱或澇。則當於道場中隱密處身著皂衣
<lb n="0459a03"/>面向南坐。以燒
<note n="0459001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">死＝屍&M062403;【原】</note>
<app n="0459001"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">屍</rdg></app>灰畫三角壇中書彼羅&CB00264;
<lb n="0459a04"/>彗星等形。旱澇時畫龍形。於彼人心上書彼人
<lb n="0459a05"/>名。於中夜及午時燒安悉香。念誦於真言。句中
<lb n="0459a06"/>加彼名以石榴枝鞭其彼形誦真言二十一遍
<lb n="0459a07"/>每一遍一鞭<note n="0459002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（天災）＋即&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0459002"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">天災即</rdg></app>除。若五星陵逼強盛命衰亦
<lb n="0459a08"/>作此法。</p></div2>
<lb n="0459a09"/><p>大聖息災真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0459a10"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛他&CB00617;多室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曳娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0459a11"/><p>破宿曜災難真言</p>
<lb n="0459a12"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>室哩曳<note place="inline">二合</note>三摩曳娑&CB00085;賀</p>
<lb n="0459a13"/><p>北斗七星真言</p>
<lb n="0459a14"/><p type="dharani">迦唎計入&CB00085;哩也波囉&CB00425;吒修智囉摩耶娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0459a15"/><note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0459a16"/><p>香用薰陸白壇可置<note n="0459003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壇＝檀&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0459003"><lem>壇</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">檀</rdg></app>樣。</p></div1>
<lb n="0459a17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>北斗七星護摩法</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0459a18"/><div1 type="W"><p>康安二年三月二十七日。於東寺坊書寫之畢。寫本不
<lb n="0459a19"/>審多之。追可挍證本矣　果寶<note place="inline">五十七</note>　天明二壬寅年
<lb n="0459a20"/>六月十二日。以東寺觀智院之本書寫之。閣筆於智積
<lb n="0459a21"/>教院南杉舍　慈忍<note place="inline">四十八</note>　觀修寺真言集云。北斗七
<lb n="0459a22"/>星護摩法一行撰。又北斗指尾法引用此。今歲求智積
<lb n="0459a23"/>院之本。校合施國字。上木藏於勸學院寶庫時享和二
<lb n="0459a24"/>壬戌年五月二日豐山長谷妙音院小池坊輪下。</p>
<lb n="0459a25"/><p>　　　　　　　　　　總持院沙門　　快道誌</p></div1>
